\b \cf0 Stretch Goals\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural

\b0 \cf0 Sign up screen (can merge login and signup into one screen as per Dribbble design)
\b \
\
Overview
\b0 \
often word of mouth referral but of bad contractors\
\
hard to get good word of mouth referral\
\
younger crowd uses yelp/angies list\
 - yelp uses subjective measures of quality\
 - angies list requires people to generate reviews/often not accurate\
\
Objective metrics rather than subjective metrics of yelp/angies\
 - web interface has grid with balls representing number of jobs completed\
 - y-axis is projected time versus real time\
 - x-axis is projected cost vs. real cost\
\
Main list view \
\
Calendar view listed by due date\
\
Click on a specific project to get sublist\
 - each sublist item has sublist item title, due date, and picture when done\
\
Trust a big issue because have to leave stranger in your home while you go to work\
 - Picture gives instant snapshot to client to ease some worries\
\
